        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks GJR for copy of his book [<hi rend="italic">Christian prayer and general laws</hi> (1874)].</p> 
            <p>Discusses breeding and sterility.</p>
            <p>Discusses experiments to test Pangenesis. Cites useful references.</p>
            <p>Suggests GJR visit Kew gardens.</p>
        </abstract>
